abstract: Stocks end mostly lower following hints by Federal Reserve of imminent interest rate hikes.

headline.print_headline: Shares Slip After Fed Hints at Rate Increase
headline.main: Wall St. Slips After Yellen Speech

snippet: Janet Yellen, the Fed chief, signaled that an interest-rate increase was likely, but she did not indicate any timetable....
lead_paragraph: Janet Yellen, the Fed chief, signaled that an interest-rate increase was likely, but she did not indicate any timetable.
